Vivid colours, weightless fabrics and surreal silhouettes – @giambattistavalliparis serves up a lucid dream this season. Key Makeup Artist @helenevasnier helped us enter into the designer’s subconscious mind with strong yet simple looks starring warm brick red lips, fresh faces and dramatic “M·A·C Black Liners.” Bring your own look to life with:
🖤Matte Lipstick in Chili
🖤Pro Longwear Fluidline in Blacktrack
🖤In Extreme Dimension 3D Black Lash
🖤Amplified Lipstick in Blankety
🖤Studio Fix Sculpt And Shape Contour Palette

@balmain hits the big screen this FW21. The French luxury fashion house presents its #BALMAINFW21 collection in the form of a five-episode drama series titled Fracture. Key Makeup Artist @kalikennedy brings the eclectic cast of characters to life with polished yet lived-in looks that mirror the mood at Le Rêve – the run-down motel that serves as their temporary home. 
 
@jessejostark wears:
•Lip Pencil in Cork
•Powder Kiss Lipstick in Impulsive
•Studio Fix 24-Hour Smooth Wear Concealer
•Prep + Prime Transparent Finishing Powder
•Studio Fix Sculpt And Shape Contour Palette
•Eye Brows Big Boost Fibre Gel in Spiked 
•Pro Face Palette: Contour
•Mixing Medium Shine

@melton wears: 
•Prep + Prime Lip
•Fast Response Eye Cream
•Fix+
#MACBackstage #FRACTURESERIES @maccosmeticsfrance @maccosmetics_mex
